      <data key="entity_type">concept</data>
      <data key="description">Confidence Threshold is a hyperparameter used in NMS to filter boxes with low scores.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidence threshold is a hyperparameter that filters prediction boxes and affects NMS execution time and accuracy.&lt;SEP&gt;Hyperparameter evaluated in Table 1 with values 0.001, 0.01, and 0.05.</data>
