      <data key="entity_id">Kongzi</data>
      <data key="entity_type">artifact</data>
      <data key="description">Kongzi is a large language model specifically designed for historical understanding and complex reasoning.&lt;SEP&gt;A model evaluated under different judges and compared with other models like Deepseek-r1 and GPT-4o.&lt;SEP&gt;Kongzi is a language model specifically designed for the historical domain.&lt;SEP&gt;Kongzi is a historical large language model with fact enhancement capabilities described in the research paper.&lt;SEP&gt;A language model proposed in the paper for the historical domain, evaluated in the table.&lt;SEP&gt;Kongzi is a historical large language model designed to address factual inaccuracies in historical reasoning.</data>
